        <p><img src="/images/welcome_to_bell_marketing.gif" alt="Welcome to Bell Marketing" /></p>

<p>We&rsquo;re proud to supply the food industry with the finest quality fruit ingredients.</p>

<p>Our sources are both foreign and domestic. Quantities are available in tankers, bins, drums, pails and cases. Our products are available ex–warehouse, ex–dock, or FOB.</p>

<p>We specialize in sourcing materials to meet your individual product specifications, and feel we can find the right product for you at competitive prices. Our principles meet your high standards for excellence, dependability, and consistent high quality.</p>

<p>Please call Bell Marketing, Inc. for all your food ingredient requirements. We will be happy to supply you with current market quotes, samples and any other required need. We look forward to hearing from you!</p>

